text: We're Not Married! is a 1952 romantic comedy movie. It was directed by Edmund Goulding. Actors include: Ginger Rogers, Fred Allen, Victor Moore, David Wayne, Eve Arden, Eddie Bracken, Mitzi Gaynor, Lee Marvin, and Zsa Zsa Gabor. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * * Category:1952 romantic comedy movies Category:American romantic comedy movies Category:Movies directed by Edmund Goulding Category:20th Century Fox movies
